{"tid":1281193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 有人買返D汽水塞爆個立法會立餐廳","createTime":"2019-07-03T08:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T08:32:50.000Z","uid":66925,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"86b0965121a64763ce0908a8277481df4c3b661b","tid":1281193,"uid":66925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/576952792/posts/10156239892997793?s=100000223950769&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F576952792%2Fposts%2F10156239892997793%3Fs%3D100000223950769%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=00fc3e74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/576952792/posts/10156239892997793?s=100000223950769&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\nOK，我代示威者講聲對唔住，應該夠㗎啦，唔洗找啦<br />\n<br />\n有佢哋contact 嘅朋友麻煩提佢哋收嘢<br />\n<br />\n//示威者衝入立法會後，裏內的餐廳亦不倖免，其所屬的嘉嘉得飲食有限公司董事李先生說，昨兩名員工隨警察入內察看，見收銀機被毁，員工儲物櫃被打開，雪櫃內凍肉散落一地，雞蛋不翼而飛，雪櫃門雖貼上「我們不是賊人，不會不問自取」字句，但櫃內飲品「被掏空」，只留下小量金錢，「那些錢明顯不夠（支付）」，形容示威者行為「野蠻、過分」。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學太陽花學運咁用汽水同雞蛋塞爆佢間餐廳有無得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26689fb0d0dce0b074e9458fddc501ffda452dcc","tid":1281193,"uid":230730,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf5f72167565747e89ff23f99d615b95b53a88bb","tid":1281193,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:26:04.000Z","msg":"解封未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf71d0e05ae281158a469593dadadcd952ceea0","tid":1281193,"uid":254183,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"26689fb0d0dce0b074e9458fddc501ffda452dcc","tid":1281193,"uid":230730,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d5H9Cta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=